174
00:09:26,310 --> 00:09:26,790
Qin.

175
00:09:27,710 --> 00:09:28,150
Xu Qin.

176
00:09:28,670 --> 00:09:28,910
My sister.

177
00:09:29,830 --> 00:09:30,470
Zhan Xiaorao.

178
00:09:30,470 --> 00:09:31,550
My ex-girlfriend.

179
00:09:32,510 --> 00:09:32,830
Hello.

180
00:09:34,070 --> 00:09:34,510
Hello.

181
00:09:36,910 --> 00:09:37,230
Brother.

182
