191
00:09:56,510 --> 00:09:57,510
You have a strong character.

192
00:09:57,830 --> 00:09:58,150
Xiao Yixiao.

193
00:09:58,150 --> 00:09:59,430
You're so nosy.

194
00:10:00,390 --> 00:10:01,230
That's none of your business.

195
00:10:02,790 --> 00:10:03,670
